<C>__{iranoff}
<D>__{we avoided luxury and extravagance and today... well, if you were to offer us a glass of champagne, we wouldn't say no.}
<A>__{leon is so engrossed in his thoughts that he overlooks the hinterior}
<C>__{leon}
<D>__{well, boys, i'd like to help you but what can i do? yesterday i waited six hours in the lobby!}
<C>__{kopalski}
